âœ¨ Mention extensibility: â€œWe can add new handlers without modifying existing ones.â€
ðŸ§© Highlight decoupling: â€œEach handler knows only about the next, not the whole pipeline.â€
ðŸ” Support dynamic handler order if needed: â€œWe can reorder handlers based on user role or configuration.â€

Extensibility: "New steps like promo code or EMI handler can be plugged in easily."
Fail-fast design: "If any step fails, transaction is halted."
Encapsulation: "Each step has its own responsibility. No giant method."
Open/Closed Principle: "No need to modify existing code when adding new validation."


